        <mxCell id="hNote" value="Two independent radios. UWB (6.5 GHz, DW3110) and BLE (2.4 GHz, nRF52833) are separate chips&lt;br&gt;in separate bands with separate antennas &#8212; there is NO RF coexistence problem between them.&lt;br&gt;All contention is for CPU attention. See page 2." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#8C93A0;align=left;spacingLeft=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#171A1F;" vertex="1" parent="h1">
